  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "TDI Kriss Vector Gen.2 9x19 冲锋枪",
      "en": "TDI KRISS Vector Gen.2 9x19 submachine gun"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Vector 9x19",
      "en": "Vector 9x19"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 105,691₽ | 物品价值: 27,800 | Mechanic报价: 15,568₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 52,562₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级3 < 96,715₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级2 < GP x18 | Σ ≈ 135,000₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 输血工具 x5 | Σ ≈ 69,755₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级4 < PSU x1 + 电源线 x3 + 电线 x6 | Σ ≈ 370,957₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Western Connection - Part 2 @ Skier\n\nKRISS Vector 冲锋枪结构紧凑、可控性好，适用于近距离作战环境，是军队和执法部门的理想选择。低枪管轴线和Super V后坐力缓冲的设计使该枪具有极佳的可控性，适用于很多射击环境，或半自动快速跟进射击。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 105,691₽ | 物品价值: 27,800 | Mechanic报价: 15,568₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 52,562₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级3 < 96,715₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级2 < GP x18 | Σ ≈ 135,000₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 输血工具 x5 | Σ ≈ 69,755₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级4 < PSU x1 + 电源线 x3 + 电线 x6 | Σ ≈ 370,957₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Western Connection - Part 2 @ Skier\n\nThe KRISS Vector SMG is the ideal choice for law enforcement and military seeking a controllable and compact weapon system for close quarter combat environments. The low bore axis and Super V recoil mitigation system allow for controllable shots when firing in full-automatic, or fast semi-automatic follow up shots. Compatible with Glock 9x19 magazines."
    },
